{"tid":1452262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有人係尖沙咀被黑警射盲眼，你地就叫人去機場，宜家興返無哩頭？","createTime":"2019-08-12T00:37:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T01:24:05.000Z","uid":241151,"like":6,"dislike":71,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"98abc05b00e1fb51f864f1fbb269d21cfba07b84","tid":1452262,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:37:15.000Z","msg":"連登左膠唔講我都唔知昨晚尖沙咀班黑警今日唔係返警署而係去做機場地勤"},{"pid":"990408623c1d76b9f38985d9bab725f93287ceda","tid":1452262,"uid":134178,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:42:39.000Z","msg":"唔好意思<br />\n借個位<br />\n<br />\n正式宣佈 &quot;Bruce.Lee&quot; P牌仔係on9<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1451717/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1451717/page/1</a><br />\n佢每一個post都係帶風向叫示威者做無撚用既野、威脅唔到政府既野<br />\n<br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 聽日唔好入機場，係局，係陷阱<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1451252/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1451252/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n-條友好中意深夜帶風向<br />\n-以前開post會有殘體字 (喜恶 痛脚 静坐 绝食)<br />\n-叫義士絕食 (大家都知絕食係玩自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n-已經被人屌過一次五毛、跟住改名 由 &quot;索羅斯&quot; 變 &quot;Bruce.Lee&quot;<br />\n-平時會開正常post，無助大局既post，例如超多個post屌鳩林鄭 <br />\n-唔記得轉ACC講&quot;幫推&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1443690/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1443690/page/1</a><br />\n知自己柒左跟住唔推post<br />\n<br />\n以前既post：<br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 打死都唔好去離境大堂，記住目的唔係要癱瘓機場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1434076/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1434076/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 【突發】機場和理非行動將有大量警犬着黑衫混入<br />\n事後：機場無事發生過，無見過有鬼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1426739/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1426739/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 唔好搞TVB呀，和平呼籲佢地罷工啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1422849/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1422849/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 你地繼續叫林鄭下台啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1417341/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1417341/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1418035/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1418035/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1417281/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1417281/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1416814/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1416814/page/1</a><br />\n事實：林鄭下台其實都無撚用<br />\n<br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 唔好登報，用啲錢做其他野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1346745/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1346745/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 唔好成立臨時政府<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1232468/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1232468/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 唔好搞G20登報，搞7.1啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1257157/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1257157/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 唔好沖(殘體字)立法會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1271370/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1271370/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 五大訴求係on9<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1305986/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1305986/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 警察可能會全面驅趕鄉黑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1342662/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1342662/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 繼續和平遊行啦~<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1353893/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1353893/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 說服警察加入遊行，感化警察<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1230663/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1230663/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 整多個G牌啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1434492/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1434492/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 【急】而家真係需要一個大台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1337502/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1337502/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBruce.Lee P牌仔 起底頁面傳送門<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/258370\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/258370</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n推上熱門"},{"pid":"589fa610fd433aafb5b2c5245deaeba6b9c533fb","tid":1452262,"uid":83998,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:43:22.000Z","msg":"繼續圍有咩意思？<br />\n又有黑衣狗 又再集人比人拉比人射？"},{"pid":"eedfacf9237bb64506bbf84dba5e898f49e4c250","tid":1452262,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:43:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ea395c1359f6f882178d886eccd005ba2817e0","tid":1452262,"uid":294844,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:44:19.000Z","msg":"冇計，唔敢還拖"},{"pid":"f3ffedbc9de5be7d9fbe363fe443027638e8e956","tid":1452262,"uid":150337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98abc05b00e1fb51f864f1fbb269d21cfba07b84","tid":1452262,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:37:15.000Z","msg":"連登左膠唔講我都唔知昨晚尖沙咀班黑警今日唔係返警署而係去做機場地勤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:44:52.000Z","msg":"因為劇本寫好咗。運動要升級。"},{"pid":"585c77ac7510690124d7b9fb5ceffb620de29d0b","tid":1452262,"uid":205043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:45:18.000Z","msg":"咁你去狗屋劈友未?"},{"pid":"1730d33090d68c9bd9d8440fb2dd832b3ff29cb0","tid":1452262,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d10cdd744ae641884b